  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "<p><strong>Aspects </strong>bloodglass, ?</p><p><strong>Minor Gifts </strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-relic-bloodglass.bloodglass-gifts.Item.gwJKM2oKeV6Jtst1]{Bloodglass Aegis}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-relic-bloodglass.bloodglass-gifts.Item.TEQDOBHZxYfcZwNc]{Radiant Stream}</p><p><strong>Major Gifts</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-relic-bloodglass.bloodglass-gifts.Item.xGy3EJ1IQxZHFRYL]{Refracted Image}, ?</p><p><strong>Grand Gifts</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-relic-bloodglass.bloodglass-gifts.Item.cIp0yJNIRHZ8GosP]{Crystal Orchid Dance}</p><p>?</p><p>Property Runes<br />- Figure out Property Runes</p><p>Fundamental Runes<br />Iúna's fundamental runes automatically upgrade at the appropriate levels.</p><p>Level 2 - @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.DKWuJb2rSgiotOG7]{Weapon Potency (+1)}</p><p>Level 4 - @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.DxCuJKynlnMQZHgp]{Striking}</p><p>Level 10 - @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.pOoEiuEuITm4I2Il]{Weapon Potency (+2)}</p><p>Level 12 - @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.KCQRFvUgbyclvOGi]{Striking (Greater)}</p><p>Level 16 - @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.rvItjGQaYT7Luwtm]{Weapon Potency (+3)}</p><p>Level 19 - @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.woxl2FrrgAcJDu0t]{Striking (Major)}</p><p>Possibly include bits of Lilandra's sword at some point? (Through Bloodglass, probably)</p>",
      "value": "<p>This bladed scarf has been carefully imbued with latent magical ability by a being with both fey and demon blood, and inhabited by a minor celestial spirit drawn to the wielder's soul. The spirit within the scarf seems most please with being called Iúna.</p>\n<p>The long black and purple silk and cloth scarf has been carefully embroidered and decorated with hundreds of handmade glass beads containing the blood of Edaranduidach, forming countless sigils.</p>\n<p>Two long, bat-like wings stretch from edge to edge in its designs, modeled after the wings of someone whom Edaranduidach loves very much, and with whom she has bound her very soul.</p>"
    },
